Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:23.54,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}我无须你的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.01,0:22:28.26,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}凛冽的寒风  把我的心冻伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.44,0:22:32.61,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}眼里燃烧着誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.23,0:22:41.40,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}现在  你我心照不宣  奋力奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.03,0:22:47.75,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}接受彼此一切的那天若是会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.75,0:22:51.65,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}坚信着那一刻的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.70,0:22:57.13,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}悲伤穿梭于整个时代
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.36,0:23:01.21,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}让我们牢记这段记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.53,0:23:06.08,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}想要触摸彼此心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.21,0:23:10.41,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}即使擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:14.90,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}也要追逐同一个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:19.00,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}化作流星
